Smash and grab raiders left expensive handbags littered across a street in central London as they fled from a robbery on a designer shop.

Luxury luggage brand Moynat's flagship store in London was the target of the break in, which occurred in the early hours of this morning.

In their hurry to flee the store following the robbery, the thieves left a number of the expensive bags - which start from around £800 - strewn across the road outside the shop in Mayfair.

