'We were called on Sunday at approximately 1.45am to reports of a burglary,' said a spokesman from the Metropolitan Police.

'Westminster Police are investigating. There have been no arrests.

'There are three suspects in total, two of them left on one moped.'

The shop was open as normal today. A spokesman for the chain was not available for comment tonight.

The value of the items taken is unknown.

